                        <span>Jesus taught us to pray for His kingdom to come and His will be done on earth as it is in heaven. We believe there is not a simpler unifying and rallying issue for the church to pray about then the welfare of children and families. Passages like 2 Chronicles 7:14 &amp; Jeremiah 29:7 talk about a God who wants to bring healing and welfare to a unified community that prays. 111Project through CarePortal requests and weekly updates is calling the church to pray about individual real time needs but then also community wide challenges. Would your church be committed to pray for transformation in child welfare?</span>
                    </div>
