                    <div class="collapsible-body">
                        <span>The scripture challenges us in Hebrews 10:24 to consider how to spur one another on to love and good deeds. We recognize this does not happen without intentionality. We ask each church to commit to recruit at least one-point person—staff or volunteer—who will interface regularly with the 111Project to help families engage and facilitate regular support of foster care initiatives within your church. This point person helps us mobilize your church to action through opportunities for praying, giving, volunteering, and opening your home in response to the child welfare crisis. 111Project uses the CarePortal platform to facilitate many of these opportunities.</span>
                    </div>
