                    </div>
                    <div class="collapsible-body">
                        <span>111Project’s CarePortal is an online platform that brings the needs of hurting children and families in your community to your attention. Caseworkers at partner agencies uncover the needs. CarePortal makes local churches aware, giving them a real-time opportunity to respond. If 1000 churches committed to assist one family in crisis every month through the 111Project CarePortal network there would be more than enough support for biological, foster, and adoptive families and the children who have found themselves in the child welfare system at no fault of their own. Learn more about opportunities and places to serve as a part of the Oklahoma network below. Could the church be seen living James 1:27 in a beautiful diverse set of ways.</span>
                    </div>
